### Variables (set in your client)
@host = http://localhost:8080
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### Register
POST {{host}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@example.com",
  "password": "secret12",
  "fullName": "Demo User"
}

### Login
# @name login
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@campus.edu",
  "password": "user123"
}

### List resources
GET {{host}}/api/resources
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List resources — filter
GET {{host}}/api/resources?type=AUDITORIUM&minCapacity=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Seat availability (auditorium id from seed)
GET {{host}}/api/resources/3/seats/availability?start=2026-01-15T10:00:00&end=2026-01-15T12:00:00
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create booking (room — use resource id 1 for Seminar Room)
POST {{host}}/api/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resourceId": 1,
  "startTime": "2026-06-01T09:00:00",
  "endTime": "2026-06-01T11:00:00",
  "purpose": "Study session",
  "attendees": 8
}

### Create booking (auditorium — replace seatIds with ids from availability response)
POST {{host}}/api/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resourceId": 3,
  "startTime": "2026-06-01T14:00:00",
  "endTime": "2026-06-01T16:00:00",
  "purpose": "Guest lecture",
  "attendees": 2,
  "seatIds": [1, 2]
}

### Approve booking
PUT {{host}}/api/bookings/1/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Approved for campus event"
}

### Reject booking
PUT {{host}}/api/bookings/1/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Room reserved for maintenance"
}

### Tickets
POST {{host}}/api/tickets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resourceId": 1,
  "description": "Projector flickering",
  "priority": "HIGH"
}

### Notifications
GET {{host}}/api/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Audit logs
GET {{host}}/api/admin/audit-logs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
